	   <tr><td colspan=2>I think your best bet here is to stay in Misty Thicket for a couple more levels. It is (IMHO) the best newbie zone around, with MoBs all the way up to level 14 or so. You can hunt spiders and young kodiaks, maybe do one of the goblin camps (use harmony to split the pull), or even do the orc camp (ditto with the harmony). You have guards nearby to back you up in case things go wrong. You have a guild nearby where you can buy your spells and train. Stay put until you get your level 14 spells- it'll be a whole 'nother world then. <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
