	   <tr><td colspan=2>I am told that the only dorfs that really adversely impact faction are the two guards near the elven merchant south of the docks. I think the guards are named Kyte (how appropriate) and Gonin. These guys are on a totally different faction than the others in BB, being on the Miners642 (?) faction which is the rogue's guild. The trouble here is that the rogue's guild is right by the bank in Kaladim, and within the aggro radius of the rogues (the rogue guild is the pagoda-looking building immediately to the left of the bank). I think you can offset this faction loss by killing the Peg Leg camp residents, as apparently these ButcherBlock Bandits compete with the Miners.<br><br>The two guards con high blue to a level 30, can hit for up to 57, and have around 800 hp. So the xp is at least marginally better than gnolls. Almost invariably, one will drop around 2pp for loot and the other drop only silver. Other bad news is that they are on some ridiculous 20 minute spawn or some such. best idea here is to off em after porting into BB on the way to better hunting grounds.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
